                                century]</origDate>
                        </origin>
                        <provenance>Censor's signatures on fol. XXX: Dominico Irosolomi[ta]no,
                            Alessandro Scipione 1597. Ownership inscription on fol. XXX: <foreign xml:lang="he">"משה אלשקר ידיע אל כאתב יצ"ו" ...לאברהם
                                למקנה".</foreign>
                        </provenance>
                        <acquisition>The MS belonged to the collection of John Selden (1584-1654),
                            lawyer and historical and linguistic scholar and it was acquired by the
                            Library in 1659.</acquisition>
                    </history>
